<!doctype html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
        <title>Ld23</title>
        <style type="text/css" media="screen">
            body {
                font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
                font-size: 10pt;
                background: #ddd;
                text-align: center;
            }
            h1 {
                text-align: center;
                text-shadow: 0 2px 1px #fff;
            }
            ul { list-style: none; }
            .cocos2d-app {
                zoom: 75%
                border: 1px solid #000;
                width: 640px;
                height: 480px;
                display: block;
                margin: 0 auto;
                -webkit-box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
                -moz-box-shadow:    0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
                -o-box-shadow:      0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
                box-shadow:         0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
                
                -webkit-touch-callout: none;
                -webkit-user-select: none;
                -khtml-user-select: none;
                -moz-user-select: none;
                -ms-user-select: none;
                user-select: none;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Ld23</h1>
        <div class="cocos2d-app">
            Loading Ld23...
            ${scripts}
        </div>
        use the keyboard to move through the world
        <br/>
        <ul>
            <li><b>W / A / D</b> - Jump / Go Left / Go Right</li>
            <li><b>S</b> - Enter building / Talk / Action</li>
            <li><b>Enter</b> - Restart map</li>
            <li><b>N</b> - Enter player-name</li>
            <li><b>F5</b> - Restart the map when the game is stuck</li>
            <li><b>Backspace</b> - Delete savegame</li>
        </ul>
        <hr/>
        check out <a href="https://nehmulos.wordpress.com"> nehmulos.wordpress.com</a> for updates!
    </body>
</html>
